{title:Steven Universe - Its Over Isnt It}
{artist:Misc Cartoons}

Like all jazzy stuff, it'll sound okay if you're playing on a uke and ignoring the numbers
and just playing major or minor chords, except for diminished chords. If you are simplifying,
+ is major, for lack of better simplification. But it'll sound a billion times better 
with the added notes and if you listen to the song to figure out the arpeggiations.

Also, this is the key that Pearl sings it in, which is C. A good guy key is Eb


